Class MObjectCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.modelio.vcore.model.MObjectCache

  • public class MObjectCache
extends Object
    Cache of model objects.

    Model objects are sorted by metaclass.

      • asCollection

        public Collection<SmObjectImpl> asCollection()
        Get the cache content as a collection.

        The returned collection is a view on the cache and reflects all changes made on it. The cache should not be modified while walking the returned collection to avoid unspecified behavior.

        Returns:
        all the cache content.
